<paragraph blockId="11.[136,1452,482,977]" pageId="11" pageNumber="140">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,491,914,940]" pageId="11" pageNumber="140">Distribution and habitat</emphasis>
:―This subspecies is endemic to Antikithira and the northern part of Gramvousa promontory, west 
<collectingRegion box="[339,395,950,976]" country="Greece" name="Kriti" pageId="11" pageNumber="140">Kriti</collectingRegion>
, where it grows mostly on coastal habitats.
